scriptinfo.init: local dsService = game:GetService('DataStoreService') local ds = dsService:GetDataStore('CompData') ds:RemoveAsync('Info') local dsPages = ds:ListVersionsAsync('Info', Enum.SortDirection.Descending) local items = dsPages:GetCurrentPage() local versionsRemoved = 0 for _, info in pairs(items) do if not info.IsDeleted then ds:RemoveVersionAsync('Info', info.Version) versionsRemoved += 1 end end local gameAnalytics = require(game.ServerStorage.GameAnalytics) gameAnalytics:addErrorEvent('Info', {severity = gameAnalytics.EGAErrorSeverity.info, message = 'Removed CompData & ' .. tostring(versionsRemoved) .. 'Versions.'})
